From: Ian Rogers <irogers@google.com>
Date: Mon, 19 May 2025 15:46:45 -0700
Subject: perf thread: Ensure comm_lock held for comm_list
Git-commit: 8f454c95817d15ee529d58389612ea4b34f5ffb3
Alt-commit: ae0756933e879a703e1a5deb701d9ec88b032ba3
Patch-mainline: v6.16-rc1
References: perf-sle16.1-v6.19-userspace-update
X-Info: ae075693 is slighly different and 8f454c95 was later reverted

Add thread safety annotations for comm_list and add locking for two
instances where the list is accessed without the lock held (in
contradiction to ____thread__set_comm()).

